  Locus:
    Page: 202
    Verse: 18
Tags:
  - Good
---
If you believe that God overrules all things for good, and only permits
apparently evil happenings for our good and the achievement of great ends
unbeknown to you, then all is well. All is well because you believe in the
Sovereignty of God.
